data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in the gorgeous & well-kept community of Sonara at Malibu Bay. This Stunning Lake View 1-story home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. Granite countertop kitchen, SS appliances. 2 car garage + room for 2 more in driveway. Imagine yourself enjoying endless sunsets over the tranquil lake! you will also find many fruit trees that add the perfect touch of natural sweetness to your outdoor experience. The community offers great amenities such as a clubhouse, Gym, pools, and many more. It's conveniently situated next to a top-notch Hospital, the Turnpike Highway, shops, and restaurants, ensuring that everything you need is within reach. One of the lowest HOAs in the area. Bring your pickiest buyer,s it won't disappoint them.
